metadata.name: Join the Church of Love
metadata.description:
Disclaimer:

(We have a strict policy: Love it or hate it!)

The "Church of Love" is a cult. You can only join if you are demonstrably willing to receive and give love. Besides that the owners of this token will receive infinite love as long as they hold it.  

All sales are final, money back policy only applies if you have paid with credit card or Palpay. Crypto is the real deal though. All rights are declined. Either you agree or you will burn in hell. We love you all!

The Preacher of Love  
(Grand Master of The Church of Love)
